rComments: Most difficult grader. If what you write isn't what she wants you'll get points off. Expects detailed descriptions and is a very particular and picky grader.

Okay. One of the most awesome french language profs at York. hands down. It shows from her manner of teaching that she genuinely cares about her students' progress. When you get anything back from her, READ her corrections since they are very relevant. Always willing to help, very dynamic, renders french an even more attractive discipline. love her

Man, i love this professor.  She is so nice and easy when it comes to marking tests/assignments.  At first, i thought she was a hard marker, but she is not.  I also enjoyed reading the French grammar book "Grevise". It taught me a lot about French grammar in general. I'm so glad i had her as my fre 172 teacher for this year.  Thanks Joanna !
